'''''Great Tomb, Hide the Secrets of Incarnations''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[Back to Earth in Evernight]].

==Steps==
# Talk with Dan Heng
# Keep moving forward deep into the cave
# (Optional) Talk to Castorice and Hysilens
# Keep moving forward, deeper into the vortex of memoria tide

